Proc/Daemontools version 0.01
=============================

This module is a Perl interface for Daemontools package. 

Daemontools was written by Dan Bernstein and is intended to control Unix/Linux 
daemons.
								    
See the Proc::Daemontools man page that was installed with this module for
information on how to use it in your perl programs.

This module was written on a machine using Daemontools 0.76. If you have and older
version of daemontools, possibly it will work also.

Please submit bug reports, patches and comments to bnegrao@engepel.com.br.

DEPENDENCIES

    1) the Daemontools package. Version 0.76 is preferred.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   1 - make sure the svscan process is running
   2 - perl Makefile.PL
   3 - make
   4 - make test
   5 - make install


